name: Phishing Incident Management - Incident Response

message.content: The Phishing Email sender: {{vars.email_sender}} has been  Blocked on the Secure Email Gateway

Automatic Alert Closure

No malicious indicators were found in the reported email. Due to this the alert was closed [ Automatically ] and no further action is required.

resource.content:
{{globalVars.Action_Icon}}

To make sure the attack failed,

Select all Indicators in the indicators TAB and

Execute Playbook : <02 - Phishing Incident Management > Indicator > BTN > Hunt Indicators on FortiSIEM >

{{globalVars.Hint_Icon}}

If an indicator TLP changes to RED this indicates a threat hunting match on SIEM. The source Asset is very likely infected. Browse to Correlation > Hunts and check the findings
